item.title: THM - What is Networking? - Walkthrough
item.description: This series of walkthroughs aims to help out complete beginners with finishing the Pre Security Path on the TryHackMe (thm)1 website. It is based on the learning content provided in the What is Networking? room. Task 1 - What is Networking? Get an initial idea about networks in computing. Question 1: What is the key term for devices that are connected together? Network Task 2 - What is the Internet? Since 1989…, has it really been that long?
